     FAL#WP71 UF  E           K        DISK
     FAL#WP73 O   F     256            DISK                      A
     E                    PLT        99  3
     E                    PUL        99  3
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  17 WKBAR
     I                                        1  16 WKCONT
     I                                        1   8 BAFIXD
     I                                        9  10 BATIMS
     I                                       11  13 BAIAFB
     I                                       14  14 BAEXT
     I                                       15  16 BAPP
     I                                       17  17 WKCD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80WKHZ
     I                                        1   40WKYY
     I                                        5   60WKMM
     I                                        7   80WKDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   60STIME
